.
My mother, replied Lydia, can be actuated by
no motive but a
wish
to promote my
happiness
.
I
esteem
you, my Lord, I
shall
ever remember
you with gratitude, but my mother has forbid me
to hold any
coversation
with you. Adieu, Sir,
I often think of you, but will never have any
