Two days after Major Renfew had
dispatched
the letter to Dorcas, he
set
forward for Wales,
accompanied by the Earl of Landaff; it was
nearly the
close
of the third day, they had arrived
within a few miles of the cottage, and had
slackened
their pace, that a
